snippet.title: Project Float - Trailer 2
snippet.description:
[Pre-Order at http://www.desura.com/games/project-float]

Project Float is a story about a boy who seems like there's something not quite right with his society, with their way of living. He feels like theres something not being told to him and nobody cares to question any strange occurrences. On his way back home, Buddy stumbles upon a horrible event which causes him to go and find out what's REALLY going on here. With the help of his new found companions the spheres and Lilly, the girl who knows her way around this island. Buddy sets off. And what he finds is something he couldn't have ever imagined.

For more information go to:
http://projectfloat.com/
http://www.moddb.com/games/project-float/

Trailer Music:
Seven Nation Army (Glitch Mob Remix) - The White Stripes
[ http://www.theglitchmob.com/music/2011/02/the-white-stripes-seven-nation-army-the-glitch-mob-remix/ ]
